        	<td style="padding-top:50px; padding-bottom:47px; padding-right:40px; padding-left:40px;">
            	<p align="center" style="font-size: 22px;color: #41a9ee;margin: 0;margin-bottom:25px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">Welcome to <br class="mobilebreak" style="display: none;">Simple Invoice, <%= @user.first_name %></p>
                <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">Simple Invoice makes it easy for freelancers to invoice and quote your clients. Take control of your finances by tracking which clients have paid you, and which invoices are still outstanding. We keep it simple and free by providing just the features freelancers need, without all the unnecessary complication.</p>
            </td>
