        	      <td width="87%" valign="top" style="padding-top:35px; padding-right:40px; padding-bottom:40px;">
                  <p style="font-size: 18px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 5px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">Upload your logo</p>
                  <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;padding: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">Upload your logo from the <a href="https://www.simpleinvoice.io/settings" style="text-decoration: none;color: #41a9ee;font-weight: 600;">settings page</a> and it will be added by default to your invoices and esimates. When creating your invoice you have the option to resize or hide your logo. </p>
<p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.simpleinvoice.io/settings" style="text-decoration: none;color: #41a9ee;font-weight: 600;">Upload logo</a></p>
                  </td>
      	      </tr>
      	    </tbody>
      	  </table>
          
          <!-- Step 2 -->
            <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-bottom:1px solid #ececec" class="step">
        	  <tbody>
        	    <tr>
        	      <td width="10%" valign="top" class="numbercell" style="color:#41a9ee; text-align:right; font-weight:400; font-size:42px; padding-top:32px;">2</td>
        	      <td width="3%" valign="top" style="padding-top:35px" class="spacercell">&nbsp;</td>
        	      <td width="87%" valign="top" style="padding-top:35px; padding-right:40px; padding-bottom:40px;">
                  <p style="font-size: 18px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 5px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">Finish your profile</p>
                  <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;padding: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">You can add additional information such as your address from the <a href="https://www.simpleinvoice.io/settings" style="text-decoration: none;color: #41a9ee;font-weight: 600;">settings page</a>. This information will be added by default when you create an invoice. This will save you from having to enter it each time, and you can easily change this information while creating an invoice. </p>
<p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 22px;color: #616060;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.simpleinvoice.io/settings" style="text-decoration: none;color: #41a9ee;font-weight: 600;">Finish profile</a></p>
                  </td>
      	      </tr>
